## Client-side flow

1. `apps/editor/src/hooks/useSitesAgent.ts` — `sendMessage()` POSTs to `/sites-agent/start` with `useCliAgent` flag
2. Opens SSE connection to `/sites-agent/stream?streamId=...`
3. Parses events into `messages`, `streamPhases`, `streamSteps`, `streamingText`
4. On `site_created` event: calls `addSiteFromConfig()` to add/update site in the editor's site list

## Configuration

| Env var | Where | Description |
|---------|-------|-------------|
| `VITE_AGENT_USE_CLI` | `apps/editor/.env` | `true` = CLI mode, `false` = SDK mode |
| `SITES_AGENT_MODEL` | orchestrator env | Model for SDK mode (default `claude-sonnet-4-6`) |
| `SITES_AGENT_MAX_BUDGET_USD` | orchestrator env | Max spend per agent run (default `2`) |
| `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` | orchestrator env | Required for SDK mode |
